    <string name="guide_msg">This is a regular hangman game, where you start out with 6 lives.\n\nYou have to guess a secret word, and you do so by guessing one letter at a time. If the letter you\'ve guessed is not in the word, you lose one of your 6 lives. If you use up all of your lives, you have lost. If you manage to guess the secret word without using all of your lives, you\'ve won!\n\nAfter you lose or win, you\'ll be redirected back to the main screen, where you can play again if desired.\n\nGood luck and have fun!</string>

